msgid "maxframe.tensor.nonzero"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.nonzero.nonzero:1 of
msgid "Return the indices of the elements that are non-zero."
msgstr "返回非零元素的索引。"

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.nonzero.nonzero:3 of
msgid ""
"Returns a tuple of tensors, one for each dimension of `a`, containing the"
" indices of the non-zero elements in that dimension. The values in `a` "
"are always tested and returned. The corresponding non-zero values can be "
"obtained with::"
msgstr ""
"返回一个元组，其中每个元素是一个 Tensor，对应 `a` 的每个维度中非零元素的"
"索引。`a` 中的值总是被测试并返回。可以通过以下方式获取对应的非零值："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.nonzero.nonzero:11 of
msgid "To group the indices by element, rather than dimension, use::"
msgstr "如果要按元素而不是维度对索引进行分组，请使用："

#: maxframe.tensor.indexing.nonzero.nonzero:15 of
msgid ""
"The result of this is always a 2-D array, with a row for each non-zero "
"element."
msgstr "结果总是一个二维数组，每一行对应一个非零元素。"

